                     <interp inst="t18280221-42-off221" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18280221-42-victim383" type="victimName">
                        Richard 
                        Giles
